About credit card skimmers and formjacki.message: About credit card skimmers and formjacking

Malicious actors can compromise online p.message: Malicious actors can compromise online purchase sites in a variety of ways, skimming their checkout pages and stealing your credit or debit card information. This is known as formjacking.

In the same way that a skimmer creates a.message: In the same way that a skimmer creates a fake front on an ATM or a public payment display, such as at a gas station, formjackers can hack into a website's back end. They can then insert code that creates a fake front on the site's payment page and capture your credit or debit card info.

Norton Safe Web's proprietary technology.message: Norton Safe Web's proprietary technology can help protect against formjacking while you shop online.
